      "id": "Master Plan",
      "kicker": "Master Plan",
      "description": "Background: I’m 20 years into building technology companies, previously the Founder of Archer ($2.7B IPO) and Vettery ($100M exit). My sole focus is Figure. My ambition is to build this company with a 30-year view, spending my time and resources on maximizing my utility impact to humanity.",
      "date": "2022-05-20T00:00:00.000Z",
